sql:
SELECT role_name, description
FROM roles
WHERE role_id > 0;

SELECT given_name, family_name, patronus, species, blood_status, wand, eye_colour, hair_colour, date_of_birth, place_of_birth, gender, height, weight, magical_abilities, ancestry, registered_date, last_updated_date, status, created_by, updated_by
FROM characters
WHERE character_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "most senior" refers to the characters with the highest IDs within each species; 
- "types" refer to the species of the characters; 
- "blood backgrounds" refer to their blood status in the magical world; 
- "workplace sections" refer to the department within the Ministry they belong to.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT ip_address
FROM access_logs
WHERE access_date = '2023-05-01';

SELECT note_text 
FROM notes 
WHERE note_id IN (0, 1);

SELECT given_name, family_name, date_of_birth
FROM characters
WHERE date_of_birth = (SELECT MIN(date_of_birth) FROM characters);

external_knowledge:
Centaur: A mythical being with the body of a horse and the head of a human;
Alphabetical Order: Sorting names from A to Z;
Mythical Beings: Creatures from folklore and mythology;
Forest of Legends: A metaphorical reference to the realm or world where mythical creatures exist.

sql:
SELECT (characters.given_name || ' ' || characters.family_name) AS "Character Full Name", users.user_name AS "Created By"
FROM characters
JOIN users ON characters.created_by = users.user_id;

SELECT DISTINCT family_name 
FROM characters 
WHERE hair_colour IN ('Black', 'Blue');
